6. src/state.rs / src/wm.rs: any `manual_let_else` warnings (e.g. `let X = match ... { Some(x) => x, None => return ... }`) — convert to `let Some(x) = ... else { return ... };` form where clippy flags it. Only change the ones clippy actually flags.

