ttons, the bottom taskbar, and the launcher menu columns via chunked `PutImage`, avoiding any compositing-manager dependency; `arrange()` dynamically grows the canvas width from leaf count and minimum split width, positions/maps off-screen clients out, and resamples the focused client's top-center pixel content to adopt its accent colour (skipped mid-drag to avoid redundant X round-trips). A `smush` system synthesizes Ctrl+0/Ctrl+- keystrokes via XTEST to auto-shrink terminal fonts in narrow splits, cached per client and width bucket. Consecutive motion events within a batch are coalesced to the most recent pointer position so drag recomposites never pile up, and the full-screen BGRX blit buffer is reused across frames via a `RefCell<Vec<u8>>` to avoid per-frame allocation. The launcher menu is implemented as two override-redirect popup windows (main column + one category submenu) with hover tracking, highlighted rows, and separator dividers, all composited through the same `draw_menu` renderer and `PutImage` blit path.
